    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Hon. Wesley L. Jones will give the\ncommencement Grafton.\n\n\nArrangements have been made\nfor the dedication of the new do\nnestle science building as a part of\nthe commencement exercises. The\ndedication will occur Wednesday\nafternoon, June II. Gov Mead is\nannounced as one of the speakers\nof the occasion. The Federation of\nWoman's Clubs of Washington will!\nbe represented by Mrs. w. H. Allen,\nof Spokane, president of that Or\nganization, who will be one of the\nspeakers."
    }
